WEBVTT

1
00:12:07.110 --> 00:12:09.170 
- 好的 那么... - 菲尔 听我说
- All right, so... - Phil, hear me out on this.

2
00:12:09.250 --> 00:12:11.850 
如果你是想说带着他一起 我同意
If it's about bringing him along with us, then yes.

3
00:12:11.880 --> 00:12:13.960 
好极了 瓦莱特 过来
Great. Wallet, get over here, buddy.

4
00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:16.320 
瓦莱特 你以前见过手机吗
Hey, Wallet, you ever see a phone before?

5
00:12:18.300 --> 00:12:19.360 
他喜欢手机
He likes that.

6
00:12:19.750 --> 00:12:21.220 
天啊 他牵着你的手
My God. He is holding your hand.

7
00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:22.970 
只是本能而已
Just intrinsically.

8
00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:25.140 
他就是看着手机然后伸手了
He's just looking at his phone and he reached up.

9
00:12:25.160 --> 00:12:26.880 
他抓着你的小指头
He's holding your pinky.

10
00:12:30.010 --> 00:12:31.990 
这不是我所期待的欢迎方式啊
Not quite the welcome I was expecting.

11
00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.870 
以为他们会有个
Thought they'd have like a branded step-and-repeat

12
00:12:33.910 --> 00:12:34.920 
品牌标志背景墙什么的
or something.

13
00:12:34.940 --> 00:12:36.680 
会有人来迎接我们对吧
Someone's gotta come welcome us, right?

14
00:12:36.700 --> 00:12:38.210 
他们说会有人来
They said there'd be someone.

